591
00:46:18,757 --> 00:46:20,297
Where are you in all this?

592
00:46:58,441 --> 00:46:59,638
Jeha...

593
00:47:01,297 --> 00:47:02,685
Jeha didn't do it

594
00:47:04,875 --> 00:47:06,049
You know that

595
00:47:15,098 --> 00:47:16,206
Jeha

596
