645
00:51:11,813 --> 00:51:13,975
Have you ever asked
where this money came from?

646
00:51:18,996 --> 00:51:21,717
You just liked it
when I spent money, all of it!

647
00:51:27,212 --> 00:51:28,421
So...

648
00:51:34,592 --> 00:51:36,216
