661
00:53:28,865 --> 00:53:30,056
That mother cat too

662
00:53:31,154 --> 00:53:32,881
Hey, that's...

663
00:53:32,882 --> 00:53:34,915
Our dad didn't know

664
00:53:36,506 --> 00:53:38,082
